Background
==========

Currently distribution specific presets are maintained using a
separate panel. On this panel these presets are provided using
a pre-populated text area. The user also would be able to add
additional parameters manually by editing the text area contents.

We discussed the following
==========================

1.

The misc panel is not needed cause it adds additional clutter
to the overall workflow.

2.

Instead the presets are automatically added to the download
param file step. There the presets are added to the text area
is it was the case on the misc panel.

Additionally the user would still be able to manually add
parameters as necessary.
